Download TCGA Data.

下载临床信息

  • 下载文件信息时，如果给予赋值，将会返回 query 值。

  • 这种写法占用过多内存，需要及时释放内存，即需要执行WGCNA::collectGarbage()。 为了使包更加轻便，本包不降武德，直接把WGCNA::collectGarbage()函数抄了过来。

library(TCGAeasy)
tcga_download_clinic("TCGA-LGG")
#> Manifest saved as: GDCdata/TCGA-LGG_Clinical_BCR_XML_gdc_manifest.txt
#> Downloading data for project TCGA-LGG
#> Of the 515 files for download 515 already exist.
#> All samples have been already downloaded
query <- tcga_download_clinic("TCGA-LGG")
#> Manifest saved as: GDCdata/TCGA-LGG_Clinical_BCR_XML_gdc_manifest.txt
#> Downloading data for project TCGA-LGG
#> Of the 515 files for download 515 already exist.
#> All samples have been already downloaded
xfiles <- list.files("GDCdata/TCGA-LGG/Clinical/", pattern = "xml", recursive = TRUE, full.names = T)
clin_patient <- tcga_xml2df(xfiles = xfiles, element = "patient", verbose = FALSE)
#> Warning in tcga_xml_parse(xfile = xfiles[x]): NAs introduced by coercion

print(clin_patient)

下载RNA seq 表达文件

  • 下载转录组定量文件时，如果给予赋值，将会返回 query 值。注意及时回收内存。
tcga_download_rna_seq_exp(project = "TCGA-LGG")
#> Manifest saved as: GDCdata/TCGA-LGG_Transcriptome_Profiling_TSV_gdc_manifest.txt
#> Downloading data for project TCGA-LGG
#> Of the 534 files for download 534 already exist.
#> All samples have been already downloaded
query <- tcga_download_rna_seq_exp(project = "TCGA-LGG")
#> Manifest saved as: GDCdata/TCGA-LGG_Transcriptome_Profiling_TSV_gdc_manifest.txt
#> Downloading data for project TCGA-LGG
#> Of the 534 files for download 534 already exist.
#> All samples have been already downloaded
print(query)
#>        results  project           data.category                      data.type
#> 1 c("e2a24.... TCGA-LGG Transcriptome Profiling Gene Expression Quantification
#>   access experimental.strategy platform sample.type barcode workflow.type
#> 1     NA                    NA       NA          NA      NA            NA
collectGarbage()

获取Count矩阵

  • 这里也包含下载功能，如果文件不存在，会自动下载。如果有结果，则会自动跳过。

  • clean_exp 是去除 HTSeq 非基因行： “N_ambiguous”,“N_multimapping”,“N_noFeature”, “N_unmapped”，同时去除以 _PAR_Y 结尾的基因ID行，目前这些基因在所有样本的检测结 果中表达量均为0.

count <- get_tcga_count("TCGA-LGG", clean = F)
